<br>
It turns out Wraith as a whole was not harassing me, just a bunch of thier members. Now, I could say names but how is that going to make things better? It will just cause people to flame specific people and totally blow things out of porportion.<br>
<br>
Now, I talked to several Gm's and guides that night, and they said there was alot of petitions against me. However they did not state how many. <br>
<br>
As for the tells I got, alot of them were nasty, some where just &quot;WTF you ninja for&quot; and that sort of thing. And some where from people in Luclin not even in Wraith calling me a &quot;ninja&quot;. Not to mention a few people who also heard somehow, saying &quot;What happened?&quot;. I started getting tells from people all over the server who heard what happened, and I was having a hard time dealing with them, plus the Wraith people sending tells.<br>
<br>
It somehow spread like wildfire, and I don't know how. I'm guessing whoever really ninja looted lighted the match and blamed it all on me.<br>
<br>
But as I said earlier, I forgive and forget, but I wish I knew who really ninja looted those arms. Which I was hopeing the post would also reveal while clearing my name.<br>
<br>
This post was in no way a Wraith bash, Im not that kind of person to bash people/guilds. I just wanted the truth.<br>
<br>
But it would appear some people would love to turn it into a anti Wraith post.... *sigh* I had enough of this topic, im done.<br>
